<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٨٥ ... سُورَةُ البُرُوجِ ... آياتها٢٢ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَاتِ الْبُرُوجِ}</span> ... ذَاتِ المَنَازِلِ الَّتِي تَمُرُّ بِهَا الشَّمْسُ، وَالقَمَرُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْيَوْمِ الْمَوْعُودِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُوَ:</span> يَوْمُ القِيَامَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشَاهِدٍ وَمَشْهُودٍ}</span> ... أَقْسَمَ اللهُ بِكُلِّ شَاهِدٍ يَشْهَدُ، وَبِكُلِّ مَنْ يُشْهَدُ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُتِلَ}</span> ... لُعِنَ، وَعُذِّبَ، وَهَلَكَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَصْحَابُ الْأُخْدُودِ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ شَقُّوا فِي الأَرْضِ شَقًّا عَظِيمًا؛ لِإِحْرَاقِ المُؤْمِنِينَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْوَقُودِ}</span> ... مَا تُشْعَلُ وَتُوقَدُ بِهِ النَّارُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شُهُودٌ}</span> ... حُضُورٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَنُوا}</span> ... حَرَّقُوا بِالنَّارِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَذَابُ الْحَرِيقِ}</span> ... العَذَابُ المُحْرِقُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَطْشَ}</span> ... انْتِقَامَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُبْدِئُ}</span> ... يَخْلُقُ الخَلْقَ ابْتِدَاءً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيُعِيدُ}</span> ... يُحْيِيهِمْ بَعْدَ مَوْتِهِمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْوَدُودُ}</span> ... المُحِبُّ لِأَوْلِيَائِهِ، المَحْبُوبُ لَهُمْ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَجِيدُ}</span> ... العَظِيمُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>